<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Order Notification</title>
<style>
body {
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

.header {
text-align: center;
background-color: #f4f4f4;
padding: 20px;
box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.header h1 {
margin: 0;
font-size: 2.5em;
color: #333;
text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

p {
font-size: 1.2em;
color: #555;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
    <h1>Modern Home</h1>
</div>
    <h1>Order Notification</h1>
    <p>Hello ${userName},</p>
    <p>Your order with code '${orderCode}' has been ${orderStatus}.</p>
    <p>You will receive your order in 2 days.</p>
    <p>Thank you for your business!</p>
</body>
</html>
